{
  "stem": "1208.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, one day, again, there were rumors that Belzyce was being dissolved and we were being sent to another camp, a harsher camp called Budzyn.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before the liquidation actually happened, some Nazis and people from the Judenrat came from a town called Krausnick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very small town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were conferring all day long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could see all this from my little hospital room, [NON-ENGLISH] as we called it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think they were looking for specialized labor, people who could build, people who could make boots.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were going to take these people with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, towards the afternoon, the Nazi party with the Judenrat stomped across the grounds and came into our hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were so drunk by then, especially the untersturmführer, who was the kommandant of this little camp in Krausnick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was totally drunken and he pointed to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was hiding behind the stove because the sight of the uniforms intimidated me, as they would anyone else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he pointed to me and he said, who is that beautiful bird?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She can come with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We need a nurse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not a nurse, Herr Untersturmführer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, who asked you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Look, she's afraid of me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She comes with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he walked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that man from the Judenrat said to me, you have no choice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have to come with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said I had a brother there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he needed me and he was ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, oh no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to come, or else I'll pay for it dearly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went that afternoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never saw that untersturmführer again until one fatal night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'll explain that later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was too drunk to even remember me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
